  "title": "Sales Coordinator (5 days / West)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Provide sales and marketing support to the Sales Team for new products and services</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing customer quotations and related documentation</li>\n  <li>Support project follow-up activities to ensure timely execution</li>\n  <li>Manage project order processing, including issuing invoices and delivery orders, as well as monitoring inventory levels</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with customers on order status and delivery schedules</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the Operations team to arrange and track deliveries</li>\n  <li>Handle purchasing activities related to customer orders</li>\n  <li>Perform other ad-hoc duties and administrative tasks as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
